{"tid":531080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲老翁摔車斷脖子　自行用頭髮固定後騎車就醫","createTime":"2018-01-16T12:17:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T17:22:25.000Z","uid":122,"like":162,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"58bf16d46fd9a86d6466fb78786f570fd4e3eb9e","tid":531080,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:17:57.000Z","msg":"澳洲維多利亞省一名73歲老農夫，上月騎腳踏車時不小心摔斷了頸骨，他竟然用自己的頭髮把頭部固定住，接著騎半公里回到家，才叫來救護車將他送醫。<br />\n<br />\n上月8日，在西吉普斯蘭(West Gippsland)經營農場的73歲老農吉姆(Jim)，騎著腳踏車出門，途中他低頭看著地上的蚱蜢，車輪突然陷進一個坑，他整個人直直撞在地上，「我的頭砸在地上，但我不覺得自己就這麼完了，我重新站起來，但我馬上知道麻煩大了，因為我的頭沒辦法保持直立了」，「而且超痛的」，但因為四下無人，吉姆找了根硬物，用自己的頭髮把頭固定住，接著騎了半公里回到家。<br />\n<br />\n吉姆到家後立刻找了救護車，將他送到醫院，醫生證實，他脊椎頂部附近的2塊椎骨已經折斷，之後手術打了4隻鋼釘，目前正逐漸康復中。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"e88721690186ea97d4f874f87a6ca2abe961275b","tid":531080,"uid":27143,"like":80,"dislike":0,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:19:13.000Z","msg":"好撚勁阿伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"767f62a2974121c93e4cd477f7f963c27b433415","tid":531080,"uid":55386,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係撚唔係呀？佢識原力咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a53fb6a17ed9c59812a672136cfd596a9f9b8df","tid":531080,"uid":63870,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"quote":{"pid":"767f62a2974121c93e4cd477f7f963c27b433415","tid":531080,"uid":55386,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係撚唔係呀？佢識原力咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"平衡到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ee97a0c4b4948bb058f11583b94b9f78c2071a","tid":531080,"uid":61334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"有冇圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82056756421a10a5741b3fef5667f24c855e89a","tid":531080,"uid":628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5c3cf41ac5e4e9c880b4c3176120fd71ab2884","tid":531080,"uid":46943,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:25:05.000Z","msg":"拎幾支粟米用一把長秀髮卷係條野度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"838c841e272dd4b32d7712a3a044c097e3cebac7","tid":531080,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:54:40.000Z","msg":"圖"},{"pid":"619d5a09e0d62e1a352c9dabb45ba3ce5962ec75","tid":531080,"uid":116516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T12:58:00.000Z","msg":"想睇圖"},{"pid":"99a32fd76e8b4d034d019fcc4f983a0eec901bd7","tid":531080,"uid":152209,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:00:42.000Z","msg":"傳說中既高登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fad3b010f3ae4cec77692ed2880d71514a34868","tid":531080,"uid":63119,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:02:58.000Z","msg":"睇親戲都係扭斷頸殺人<br />\n原來咁係唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b210fc194fd528e5f6cdb810fe956eff3a40e6a2","tid":531080,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 外星人"},{"pid":"06cf96731746d187610a5ae3849c950eec1cabc3","tid":531080,"uid":127347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"ce00035c61b436c2eb73050893f41342634130d1","tid":531080,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:09:45.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9db85f1045d3ed76ac567caaad180660dce73af9","tid":531080,"uid":65074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊個連登仔黎  快d出黎認左佢"},{"pid":"1070a93e2f1f6c937107ab49cd2fed86e3a9dd4c","tid":531080,"uid":113006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:31:28.000Z","msg":"角都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a838b13ee12e597dc7d4bf5618f5bf95e846fdd","tid":531080,"uid":5056,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9db85f1045d3ed76ac567caaad180660dce73af9","tid":531080,"uid":65074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:25:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊個連登仔黎  快d出黎認左佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:48:24.000Z","msg":"阿伯: 而家個頭梗左，上唔到連登"},{"pid":"49f34d1e2cc626b7c8269170ccd0b7a283df7ca9","tid":531080,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":43,"score":-41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"古代都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n據說有的人頭被割掉還可以長好。唐肅宗至德年間，太原人王穆為魯旻部將，在南陽和安史之亂的叛兵作戰時頸部被敵兵砍了一刀，昏迷倒地，頸骨和皮肉都砍斷了，只有喉管把頭和身體連在一起。不久，他醒過來了，開始他未意識到自己已死，覺得想吃東西時，才發現頭垂在腹部。他用力把頭扶到脖頸上放好，但一鬆手頭又垂下來了。他再次把頭扶正，用一隻手掌抓牢，另一隻手解開頭髮，分別繫在兩側肩臂上。此時他的戰馬沒有離去，他掙扎著上馬時，頭又掉了下來，於是又昏厥過去。再次醒來時，發現馬在他面前臥倒，他這才騎上馬背。剛行不遠，他的部下找到了他，扶歸大營，把頭固定並包紮停當，休養了二百多天，傷口完全癒合，神志清醒如常，只是頭稍微向一側偏斜，脖子上留下一圈指頭粗的疤痕。"},{"pid":"c319467b6cba83652565e930cc5a5848a8686a35","tid":531080,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請受小生一拜"},{"pid":"48b9d76c1e5469a2d02580b043a2ee09452ceef5","tid":531080,"uid":15120,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:54:16.000Z","msg":"他知道哭是沒有用的"},{"pid":"a4ac313f99399010612fc900a2015894edb25575","tid":531080,"uid":139716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49f34d1e2cc626b7c8269170ccd0b7a283df7ca9","tid":531080,"uid":49197,"like":2,"dislike":43,"score":-41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:51:29.000Z","msg":"古代都有啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n據說有的人頭被割掉還可以長好。唐肅宗至德年間，太原人王穆為魯旻部將，在南陽和安史之亂的叛兵作戰時頸部被敵兵砍了一刀，昏迷倒地，頸骨和皮肉都砍斷了，只有喉管把頭和身體連在一起。不久，他醒過來了，開始他未意識到自己已死，覺得想吃東西時，才發現頭垂在腹部。他用力把頭扶到脖頸上放好，但一鬆手頭又垂下來了。他再次把頭扶正，用一隻手掌抓牢，另一隻手解開頭髮，分別繫在兩側肩臂上。此時他的戰馬沒有離去，他掙扎著上馬時，頭又掉了下來，於是又昏厥過去。再次醒來時，發現馬在他面前臥倒，他這才騎上馬背。剛行不遠，他的部下找到了他，扶歸大營，把頭固定並包紮停當，休養了二百多天，傷口完全癒合，神志清醒如常，只是頭稍微向一側偏斜，脖子上留下一圈指頭粗的疤痕。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:54:24.000Z","msg":"睇到好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf2559a436092dbe64ac6b3987ff71e7e943c528","tid":531080,"uid":10398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T13:55:36.000Z","msg":"斷頸都仲郁得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3312ab477329fa204dab5d2f9d61c3f4e928b9","tid":531080,"uid":90166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"我理解唔到點用頭髮固定個頭"},{"pid":"c5d0503bf9ce0aa0e83e7b0323d084035a6ff2e1","tid":531080,"uid":148399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:04:32.000Z","msg":"因為四下無人，吉姆找了根硬<br />\n<br />\ngm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個監視器香左"},{"pid":"6fec478c9bb5dc43ef484c5aadcba4170b6ab2ea","tid":531080,"uid":140057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"外星人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}